Mr. Chesnutt began his career as a CPA at Price Waterhouse where he provided accounting and financial advisory services to Fortune 500 clients in a variety of industries. Mr. Chesnutt received a BS degree from The Citadel and an MBA from Harvard Business School. He is a member of the Young Presidents' Organization.

